          <p style="color:#64748b;line-height:1.8;font-size:.93rem">S3KN Software Solutions is an Indian technology company incorporated in 2021, headquartered in Mysuru, Karnataka. We build software products and provide IT services and business process outsourcing to clients across India and globally.</p>
          <p style="color:#64748b;line-height:1.8;font-size:.93rem">GP MNREGA is our flagship product — built out of first-hand understanding of the challenges faced by Gram Panchayat officers in Karnataka.</p>
          <div class="row g-3 mt-1">
            <div class="col-md-6"><div class="p-3 rounded-3" style="background:#f0fdf4;border:1px solid #bbf7d0"><h6 style="font-weight:700;color:#15803d;margin-bottom:6px"><i class="bi bi-eye-fill me-1"></i>Our Vision</h6><p style="font-size:.84rem;color:#374151;margin:0">To be the technology partner of choice for government and enterprise customers — enabling long-term sustainable growth.</p></div></div>
